;skin=vector\"/>\n<meta name=\"generator\" content=\"MediaWiki 1.32.5\"/>\n<meta name=\"description\" content=\"A potion of enlightenment is a type of potion that appears in NetHack.\"/>\n<link rel=\"image_src\" href=\"/images/6/65/Nethackwiki-logo.png\"/>\n<link rel=\"shortcut icon\" href=\"/images/6/64/Favicon.ico\"/>\n<link rel=\"search\" type=\"application/opensearchdescription+xml\" href=\"/opensearch_desc.php\" title=\"NetHackWiki\"/>\n<link rel=\"EditURI\" type=\"application/rsd+xml\" href=\"https://nethackwiki.com/api.php?action=rsd\"/>\n<link rel=\"canonical\" href=\"/wiki/Potion_of_enlightenment\"/>\n<!--[if lt IE 9]><script src=\"/load.php?debug=false&amp;lang=en&amp;modules=html5shiv&amp;only=scripts&amp;skin=vector&amp;sync=1\"></script><![endif]-->\n</head>\n<body class=\"mediawiki ltr sitedir-ltr mw-hide-empty-elt ns-0 ns-subject page-Potion_of_enlightenment rootpage-Potion_of_enlightenment skin-vector action-view\">\t\t<div id=\"mw-page-base\" class=\"noprint\"></div>\n\t\t<div id=\"mw-head-base\" class=\"noprint\"></div>\n\t\t<div id=\"content\" class=\"mw-body\" role=\"main\">\n\t\t\t<a id=\"top\"></a>\n\t\t\t<div class=\"mw-indicators mw-body-content\">\n</div>\n<h1 id=\"firstHeading\" class=\"firstHeading\" lang=\"en\">Potion of enlightenment</h1>\t\t\t<div id=\"bodyContent\" class=\"mw-body-content\">\n\t\t\t\t<div id=\"siteSub\" class=\"noprint\">From NetHackWiki</div>\t\t\t\t<div id=\"contentSub\"></div>\n\t\t\t\t<div id=\"jump-to-nav\"></div>\t\t\t\t<a class=\"mw-jump-link\" href=\"#mw-head\">Jump to navigation</a>\n\t\t\t\t<a class=\"mw-jump-link\" href=\"#p-search\">Jump to search</a>\n\t\t\t\t<div id=\"mw-content-text\" lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\" class=\"mw-content-ltr\"><div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><div class=\"languages\"><b><a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">English</a></b>\n<p><span></span>\n<span></span>\n<span></span>\n<span></span>\n</p>\n&#160;&#8226;&#32;<span lang=\"zh-CN\"><a href=\"/wiki/Potion_of_enlightenment/zh-CN\" title=\"Potion of enlightenment/zh-CN\">中文（中国大陆）‎</a></span></div>\n<div class=\"thumb tright\">\n<table class=\"prettytable\" style=\"margin: 0;\">\n<tbody><tr>\n<th colspan=\"2\"><span class=\"nhsym clr-brightmagenta\">!</span> <a href=\"/wiki/File:Pink_potion.png\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"Pink potion.png\" src=\"/images/7/79/Pink_potion.png\" width=\"16\" height=\"16\" /></a>\n</th></tr>\n<tr>\n<th>Name\n</th>\n<td>enlightenment\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<th>Appearance\n</th>\n<td><a href=\"/wiki/Randomised_appearance\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Randomised appearance\">random</a>\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<th>Base price\n</th>\n<td>200 <a href=\"/wiki/Zorkmid\" title=\"Zorkmid\">zm</a>\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<th>Weight\n</th>\n<td>20\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<th>Monster use\n</th>\n<td><small><i>Will not be used by monsters.</i></small>\n</td></tr></tbody></table>\n</div>\n<p>A <b>potion of enlightenment</b> is a type of <a href=\"/wiki/Potion\" title=\"Potion\">potion</a> that appears in <i><a href=\"/wiki/NetHack\" title=\"NetHack\">NetHack</a></i>.\n</p>\n<div id=\"toc\" class=\"toc\"><input type=\"checkbox\" role=\"button\" id=\"toctogglecheckbox\" class=\"toctogglecheckbox\" style=\"display:none\" /><div class=\"toctitle\" lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\"><h2>Contents</h2><span class=\"toctogglespan\"><label class=\"toctogglelabel\" for=\"toctogglecheckbox\"></label></span></div>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-1\"><a href=\"#Generation\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Generation</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-2\"><a href=\"#Description\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Description</span></a>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-3\"><a href=\"#Alchemy\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2.1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Alchemy</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-4\"><a href=\"#Strategy\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Strategy</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-5\"><a href=\"#History\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">4</span> <span class=\"toctext\">History</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-6\"><a href=\"#Messages\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">5</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Messages</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-7\"><a href=\"#Variants\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">6</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Variants</span></a>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-8\"><a href=\"#UnNetHack\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">6.1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">UnNetHack</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-9\"><a href=\"#Hack.27EM\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">6.2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Hack'EM</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-10\"><a href=\"#References\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">7</span> <span class=\"toctext\">References</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Generation\">Generation</span></h2>\n<p>The potion of enlightenment makes up 2% of randomly-generated potions.\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Description\">Description</span></h2>\n<dl><dd><div class=\"noprint relarticle mainarticle\"><i>Main article: <a href=\"/wiki/Enlightenment\" title=\"Enlightenment\">Enlightenment</a></i></div></dd></dl>\n<p><a href=\"/wiki/Quaff\" title=\"Quaff\">Quaffing</a> a non-cursed <a href=\"/wiki/Exercise\" title=\"Exercise\">exercises</a> <a href=\"/wiki/Wisdom\" title=\"Wisdom\">wisdom</a> and provides <a href=\"/wiki/Enlightenment\" title=\"Enlightenment\">enlightenment</a>, allowing you to momentarily see your character's <a href=\"/wiki/Intrinsic\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Intrinsic\">intrinsics</a> and other attributes.<sup id=\"cite_ref-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup> A blessed potion additionally increases <a href=\"/wiki/Intelligence\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Intelligence\">intelligence</a> and wisdom by 1.<sup id=\"cite_ref-2\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup>\n</p><p>Quaffing a cursed potion abuses wisdom and prints a message with no other effect, prompting you to type-<a href=\"/wiki/Name\" title=\"Name\">name</a> the potion.<sup id=\"cite_ref-3\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-3\">&#91;3&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h3><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Alchemy\">Alchemy</span></h3>\n<p><a href=\"/wiki/Dipping\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Dipping\">Dipping</a> to mix together a <a href=\"/wiki/Potion_of_confusion\" title=\"Potion of confusion\">potion of confusion</a> and either a <a href=\"/wiki/Potion_of_gain_level\" title=\"Potion of gain level\">potion of gain level</a> or a <a href=\"/wiki/Potion_of_gain_energy\" title=\"Potion of gain energy\">potion of gain energy</a> has a <sup>3</sup>&#8260;<sub>10</sub> chance of producing potions of enlightenment.\n</p><p>Mixing a <a href=\"/wiki/Potion_of_levitation\" title=\"Potion of levitation\">potion of levitation</a> with a potion of enlightenment has a <sup>3</sup>&#8260;<sub>5</sub> chance of producing a <a href=\"/wiki/Potion_of_gain_level\" title=\"Potion of gain level\">potion of gain level</a>.\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Strategy\">Strategy</span></h2>\n<p>Potions of enlightenment are sometimes worth blessing to increase your mental stats. Otherwise, they are frequently saved for <a href=\"/wiki/Alchemy\" title=\"Alchemy\">alchemy</a> once identified to use in creating potions of gain level.\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"History\">History</span></h2>\n<p>The potion of enlightenment first appears in <a href=\"/wiki/NetHack_3.0.0\" title=\"NetHack 3.0.0\">NetHack 3.0.0</a>.\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Messages\">Messages</span></h2>\n<dl><dt><span id=\"You_have_an_uneasy_feeling...\">You have an uneasy feeling...</span></dt>\n<dd>You quaffed a cursed potion of enlightenment.</dd></dl>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Variants\">Variants</span></h2>\n<h3><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"UnNetHack\">UnNetHack</span></h3>\n<p>In <a href=\"/wiki/UnNetHack\" title=\"UnNetHack\">UnNetHack</a>, there is a <sup>3</sup>&#8260;<sub>5</sub> chance of a potion of enlightenment generating in the <a href=\"/wiki/Boulder\" title=\"Boulder\">boulder</a>-blocked stash on the last floor of the <a href=\"/wiki/Dragon_Caves\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Dragon Caves\">Dragon Caves</a> at level creation.\n</p>\n<h3><span id=\"Hack'EM\"></span><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Hack.27EM\">Hack'EM</span></h3>\n<p>In <a href=\"/wiki/Hack%27EM\" title=\"Hack&#39;EM\">Hack'EM</a>, the last floor of <a href=\"/wiki/The_Wyrm_Caves\" title=\"The Wyrm Caves\">The Wyrm Caves</a> uses the last floor map from the Dragon Caves of UnNetHack, including the <sup>3</sup>&#8260;<sub>5</sub> chance of generating a potion of enlightenment in the stash.\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span></h2>\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-1\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a class=\"external text\" href=\"https://github.com/NetHack/NetHack/blob/NetHack-3.6.7_Released/src/potion.c#L713\">src/potion.c in NetHack 3.6.7, line 713</a>\n     </span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-2\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-2\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a class=\"external text\" href=\"https://github.com/NetHack/NetHack/blob/NetHack-3.6.7_Released/src/potion.c#L719\">src/potion.c in NetHack 3.6.7, line 719</a>\n     </span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-3\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-3\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a class=\"external text\" href=\"https://github.com/NetHack/NetHack/blob/NetHack-3.6.7_Released/src/potion.c#L716\">src/potion.c in NetHack 3.6.7, line 716</a>\n     </span>\n</li>\n</ol></div>\n<div style=\"display:none; right:10px; padding-botto